msgctxt "sn13.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "1. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 5. Pathavīsutta → paṭhavisuttaṃ (bj) | paṭhavī 1 (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn13.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Pathavīsutta "
msgstr "5. The Earth "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.136, sc1
msgctxt "sn13.5:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: mahāpathaviyā → mahāpaṭhaviyā (bj, s1-3, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn13.5:1.2"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso mahāpathaviyā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā upanikkhipeyya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose a person was to place seven clay balls the size of jujube seeds on the great earth. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.5:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn13.5:1.4"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yā vā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā upanikkhittā yā vā mahāpathavī”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the seven clay balls the size of jujube seeds, or the great earth?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn13.5:2.1"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ mahāpathavī; "
msgstr "“Sir, the great earth is certainly more. "

msgctxt "sn13.5:2.2"
msgid "appamattikā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā upanikkhittā. "
msgstr "The seven clay balls the size of jujube seeds are tiny. "

msgctxt "sn13.5:2.3"
msgid "Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti mahāpathaviṃ upanidhāya satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā upanikkhittā”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the great earth, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.5:2.4"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave … pe … "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple, the suffering that’s over and done with is more …” "

msgctxt "sn13.5:2.5"
msgid "dhammacakkhupaṭilābho”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.5:2.6"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

